center of consciousness

00:02:39.070 --> 00:02:40.830 align:middle line:10%
studies over there.

00:02:40.830 --> 00:02:45.071 align:middle line:10%
So I'm affiliated with
them since a year now.

00:02:45.071 --> 00:02:46.570 align:middle line:84%
>>LILOU: And I know
