you tell us first why
there's a difference

00:07:22.430 --> 00:07:23.570 align:middle line:90%
in the title over there?

00:07:23.570 --> 00:07:25.420 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAUREGARD: Well,
because Brain Wars--

00:07:25.420 --> 00:07:30.080 align:middle line:84%
it was chosen by the editor
of the book at HarperCollins.

00:07:30.080 --> 00:07:33.900 align:middle line:90%


