00:30:12.040 --> 00:30:16.420 align:middle line:84%
to the activity of the pineal
gland, which is located

00:30:16.420 --> 00:30:19.110 align:middle line:90%
at the very center of the brain.

00:30:19.110 --> 00:30:21.510 align:middle line:84%
And according to
spiritual tradition,

00:30:21.510 --> 00:30:24.220 align:middle line:84%
various spiritual
traditions, it's

00:30:24.220 --> 00:30:27.110 align:middle line:84%
a very important center
for spiritual states

00:30:27.110 --> 00:30:28.400 align:middle line:90%
and experiences.

00:30:28.400 --> 00:30:33.600 align:middle line:84%
But there's not any
study yet regarding

00:30:33.600 --> 00:30:36.130 align:middle line:90%
this specific question.

00:30:36.130 --> 00:30:40.820 align:middle line:84%
>>LILOU: And to tap in this
power and this consciousness,

00:30:40.820 --> 00:30:44.370 align:middle line:84%
so we are playing a major
role in that, right?

00:30:44.370 --> 00:30:47.220 align:middle line:84%
I mean, otherwise, it's
really the person experiencing

00:30:47.220 --> 00:30:48.750 align:middle line:84%
what they say in
quantum physics.

00:30:48.750 --> 00:30:52.260 align:middle line:84%
It depends really on the
person observing and living it

00:30:52.260 --> 00:30:53.970 align:middle line:84%
that will make the
whole difference.

00:30:53.970 --> 00:30:56.500 align:middle line:84%
So how do you go,
and I'm sure you

00:30:56.500 --> 00:30:58.000 align:middle line:84%
had many debates
about this, but how

00:30:58.000 --> 00:31:00.360 align:middle line:84%
do you go to make
a skeptic see it?

00:31:00.360 --> 00:31:02.990 align:middle line:90%


00:31:02.990 --> 00:31:04.110 align:middle line:90%
Where's the transition?

00:31:04.110 --> 00:31:06.970 align:middle line:84%
Where does the
transition takes place?

00:31:06.970 --> 00:31:09.570 align:middle line:84%
>>BEAUREGARD: Well, in
the case of skeptics,

00:31:09.570 --> 00:31:12.410 align:middle line:90%
it's very difficult.

00:31:12.410 --> 00:31:14.400 align:middle line:90%
But there are exceptions.

00:31:14.400 --> 00:31:17.550 align:middle line:84%
There was a very famous
skeptical philosopher

00:31:17.550 --> 00:31:20.950 align:middle line:84%
