after this experience.

00:31:28.490 --> 00:31:30.940 align:middle line:84%
And there are other
cases, as well.

00:31:30.940 --> 00:31:34.690 align:middle line:84%
But the experience has to
be a very, very intense.

00:31:34.690 --> 00:31:38.630 align:middle line:84%
In those cases,
however, these people

00:31:38.630 --> 00:31:41.300 align:middle line:84%
