something like that.

00:31:41.300 --> 00:31:42.980 align:middle line:90%
So it happened.

00:31:42.980 --> 00:31:46.780 align:middle line:84%
Perhaps it happened for a
reason that was important,

00:31:46.780 --> 00:31:48.720 align:middle line:84%
in terms of their own
spiritual evolution.

00:31:48.720 --> 00:31:50.820 align:middle line:90%
But how do we know?

00:31:50.820 --> 00:31:54.310 align:middle line:84%
But in other cases, in
the general population,

00:31:54.310 --> 00:31:58.900 align:middle line:84%
