So in order to do that, you can
use all sorts of techniques.

00:32:09.190 --> 00:32:12.565 align:middle line:84%
Meditation will do that,
to a certain extent.

00:32:12.565 --> 00:32:15.190 align:middle line:84%
>>LILOU: But you have to have a
minimum open to try meditation.

00:32:15.190 --> 00:32:16.106 align:middle line:90%
>>BEAUREGARD: Exactly.

00:32:16.106 --> 00:32:19.360 align:middle line:84%
But if you don't have the
openness to do this, of course,

00:32:19.360 --> 00:32:21.820 align:middle line:90%
no, you won't get there.

00:32:21.820 --> 00:32:23.385 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:32:23.385 --> 00:32:27.570 align:middle line:84%
>>LILOU: Is there some
techniques or some things

00:32:27.570 --> 00:32:30.200 align:middle line:84%
that are not yet
recognized or approved

00:32:30.200 --> 00:32:35.650 align:middle line:84%
by traditional science that
show us-- that could be really

