00:32:38.000 --> 00:32:39.770 align:middle line:90%
that would be kind of the door.

00:32:39.770 --> 00:32:42.300 align:middle line:84%
I mean even telepathy
or remote viewing

00:32:42.300 --> 00:32:44.280 align:middle line:84%
or is there some that
are closer than others

00:32:44.280 --> 00:32:50.500 align:middle line:84%
that could show them or us
