00:32:55.550 --> 00:33:01.210 align:middle line:84%
And so drugs that lead you
to bring you closer to God,

00:33:01.210 --> 00:33:04.940 align:middle line:84%
if you take the root of
this word or the deity

00:33:04.940 --> 00:33:08.890 align:middle line:84%
at the origin of everything,
the source of the universe.

00:33:08.890 --> 00:33:13.400 align:middle line:84%
So these substances
will alter or will

00:33:13.400 --> 00:33:16.310 align:middle line:84%
affect the filter
function of the brain.

00:33:16.310 --> 00:33:21.560 align:middle line:84%
And so it won't allow the
brain to operate as usual.

00:33:21.560 --> 00:33:24.660 align:middle line:84%
And because it shifts the
activity in your brain,

00:33:24.660 --> 00:33:29.170 align:middle line:84%
then you can access-- it's like
if you would have a TV set,

00:33:29.170 --> 00:33:30.960 align:middle line:84%
for instance, and
you are-- normally,

00:33:30.960 --> 00:33:35.280 align:middle line:84%
we are always using
the same channels.

00:33:35.280 --> 00:33:37.320 align:middle line:84%
We're watching
the same channels.

00:33:37.320 --> 00:33:40.500 align:middle line:84%
So you have to-- and
these channels correspond

00:33:40.500 --> 00:33:43.100 align:middle line:84%
to a certain frequency,
electromagnetically.

00:33:43.100 --> 00:33:46.370 align:middle line:84%
So we are receiving certain
electromagnetic waves.

00:33:46.370 --> 00:33:52.000 align:middle line:84%
But if you were able to switch
to other electromagnetic waves

00:33:52.000 --> 00:33:56.250 align:middle line:84%
or frequencies, in other words
to switch to other channels,

00:33:56.250 --> 00:33:59.880 align:middle line:84%
