00:34:03.900 --> 00:34:11.219 align:middle line:84%
I'm talking about, for instance,
DMT and stuff like that, LSD,

00:34:11.219 --> 00:34:12.810 align:middle line:90%
mescaline.

00:34:12.810 --> 00:34:16.429 align:middle line:84%
And now these
